{
  "id": "adv_card_kor_51_01",
  "title": "fran",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "franさ～ん。聞きましたわよ！",
      "startTime": 1.6999999166,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "もうすぐ、franさんのお誕生日……あら？",
      "startTime": 4.7666665833,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_letter-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4833.333416699999,
          "startTime": 9.6
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "この先生も違う……こっちの先生もイメージとは……\nはぁ……この調子で誕生日までに間に合うのかしら……",
      "startTime": 16.2333332499,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "何か悩み事ですの？　って……まぁ！\n漫画の本がこんなに沢山。一体どうしたんですの？",
      "startTime": 26.1333332499,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "え？　あー、気にしないで。今度の『ミラクル☆\nアイドルバースデー！』で使う資料だから",
      "startTime": 36.4666665833,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "それって、アイドルがやってみたいことを叶えてくれる\n雑誌のお誕生日企画ですわよね",
      "startTime": 43.3333368104,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "franさんにもお話が来たんですのね！\nどんなお願いをするんですの？　この漫画と関係が？",
      "startTime": 49.4333350302,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "ああもう、忙しいんだから絡まないでよ……\n分かったから。説明してあげるから静かにして",
      "startTime": 58.6000016969,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど、『漫画の原作に挑戦したい』……\nそれがfranさんのやってみたいことですのね",
      "startTime": 70.8333329957,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ、それで絵を描いてくれる人を探してたって訳\nせっかくなら、好きな先生に頼みたいでしょ",
      "startTime": 79.2333329957,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "そうですわね。自分の考えたお話を、大好きな先生が\n漫画にしてくれる。夢のようなお願いですわ！",
      "startTime": 87.9333329957,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "有名な漫画雑誌を出してる出版社だし、もともと私も\n漫画が好きだから。ちょうどいいなって思ったのよ",
      "startTime": 96.1333340129,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "でも、漫画がお好きだったなんて、初めて知りましたわ\nここにある漫画も、たぶん私物ですわよね？",
      "startTime": 104.9000006796,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "い、今まで公表しにくかったのよ。漫画が好きとか\nオタクっぽいっていうか……イメージと違うかなって",
      "startTime": 114.2666673463,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことはないと思いますけど……\nでも、それならなぜ今になって……？",
      "startTime": 123.1333340129,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "最近タレントさんの中にも、普通に公表してる人がいる\nでしょ？　しかもそれが、人気に繋がっていたりするし",
      "startTime": 130.5000006796,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "なら私も、公表してもいいんじゃないかって思って\nそれに、特に最近は、ほら……kanaが話題だし……",
      "startTime": 139.9333340129,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、漫画原作の映画に出たのを機に\n漫画好きを公表していたような……？",
      "startTime": 151.4000006796,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "よく、漫画の感想をSNSに投稿してますし\n漫画関係のイベントにも呼ばれていましたわね",
      "startTime": 159.0000016969,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "そう！　それが許せないのもあって決断したのよ\n前から漫画が好きだった？　漫画はよく読む方？",
      "startTime": 166.5333350302,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-kor010.m4a",
      "text": "漫画なんてろくに読んでなかったくせして嘘ばっかり\nあんな媚び売ってるだけのにわかは、爆発するべきよ",
      "startTime": 175.1666683635,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-kor011.m4a",
      "text": "この機会に、私が話題も仕事も根こそぎ奪って\nなんちゃって漫画好きのクソガキに鉄槌を下してやるわ",
      "startTime": 182.7333350302,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "漫画への愛情は伝わってきましたが、それ以上に\n私怨が凄いですわね……。が、頑張ってくださいまし",
      "startTime": 190.4333350302,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-kor012.m4a",
      "text": "伝わった？　じゃあ説明代、千円ね\nわざわざ手を止めて、相手してあげたんだし",
      "startTime": 200.1000016969,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "こんなことでお金を要求しないでくださいまし！？\nあと、お金が掛かるなら事前に説明してくださいまし！",
      "startTime": 207.1433233065,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――その日の夜",
      "startTime": 212.484897435,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1481.7710119000083,
          "startTime": 213.9666684469
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-night",
      "startTime": 213.5515702052
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-suz013.m4a",
      "text": "ただいま戻りましたわ～\n……って、franさん、まだいらっしゃいましたのね",
      "startTime": 218.3000088177,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-kor013.m4a",
      "text": "仕方ないでしょ、全然描いてくれる先生が決まらない\nんだから。いい先生がいても、予定が合わないし……",
      "startTime": 227.1666754844,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-kor014.m4a",
      "text": "編集部があげてくれる候補は、イメージと違ったりして\n悩ましいったらないわ。……あ、それよりすず、千円",
      "startTime": 236.1666754844,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-suz014.m4a",
      "text": "さらっと請求しないでくださいまし……\nでも、それならいい案がありますわ！",
      "startTime": 245.6333360476,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-suz015.m4a",
      "text": "絵は、この私に任せるというのはどうでしょう\nなんと私は、絵のコンクールで金賞を取った実力者――",
      "startTime": 253.5666704815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-kor015.m4a",
      "text": "あー、すず、やっぱり千円は今度でいいわ\nもう帰っていいわよ",
      "startTime": 262.1666632774,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-suz016.m4a",
      "text": "聞かなかったことにしないでくださいまし！\n仕方ないですわね、では私の絵をお見せしますわ",
      "startTime": 266.8999783002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-suz017.m4a",
      "text": "これを見て下さい\n私が美術の宿題で描いた水彩画ですわ",
      "startTime": 274.2333116336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_balcony-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "balcony-00-noon",
      "startTime": 278.8316468041
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_balcony-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "balcony-00-noon",
      "startTime": 278.8316468041
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_balcony-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "balcony-00-noon",
      "startTime": 279.0983
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-night",
      "startTime": 282.3983236432
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-kor016.m4a",
      "text": "へー……まぁ、確かに中学生にしてはうまいけど\n風景画じゃない。漫画の絵とは違うわよ？",
      "startTime": 288.7666368287,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-suz018.m4a",
      "text": "そ、それは一理ありますが、練習すれば描けますわ！\nこれだけの画力があれば、漫画の絵だって余裕です",
      "startTime": 298.099970162,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
